text: Aidomaggiore (Aidumajòre, Bidumajòre) is a town and comune (municipality) in the Province of Oristano in Sardinia, Italy. As of 2016, 451 people lived there. Its area is 41.21 km². It is 250 meters above sea level. == References == == Other websites == Category:Communes of the Province of Oristano
title: Aidomaggiore
